{"tid":1384681,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有乘客理解不合作運動 有人不認同阻礙上班","createTime":"2019-07-30T02:37:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T03:36:49.000Z","uid":212626,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"5b6bc6c34bc6ddbd9c65af03f4dd1c4fa88c6e60","tid":1384681,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:37:16.000Z","msg":"有市民早上在港鐵調景嶺站阻礙列車開出，目前觀塘至調景嶺站的服務暫停，港鐵提供多輛免費接駁巴士，前往藍田、觀塘及油塘站，港鐵增派人手協助。<br />\n<br />\n現場所見，至少過百名乘客在接駁巴士站排隊候車，現場亦泊有多架免費接駁巴士準備接載乘客。<br />\n<br />\n有前往黃大仙上班的乘客表示，理解今日的運動，因為他們都有付出，希望政府站出來回應市民訴求，不要再躲起來。<br />\n<br />\n同樣轉乘接駁巴士去上班的乘客就感到憤怒，不認同是次運動，認為要給予時間政府決定，不是說要改就可以立即改。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1471316-20190730.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1471316-20190730.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=HYT0XJgSPTYEb9NwUTCrmn8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=0979094e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1471316-20190730.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=8a08d265\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1471316-20190730.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"e4a02c8bdb5df85ba6d1e3bf0da5e08f1fd45636","tid":1384681,"uid":194298,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:38:14.000Z","msg":"仲有人講我出給予時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比到2047好唔好"},{"pid":"2b826f301b7c6aae55da98c08609042dcc3ff0e4","tid":1384681,"uid":51932,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:38:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認為要給予時間政府決定，不是說要改就可以立即改</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲俾唔夠呀，過多兩年好冇"},{"pid":"4a51ff02914c0564b4b13d678be33d0badcf0fdd","tid":1384681,"uid":163789,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:39:31.000Z","msg":"D廢中廢老平時咁多打壓都忍到<br />\n今日咁樣就爆晒粗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces